2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Benson-Boone">本森·布恩（Benson Boone）</a>开放了关于摩门教徒成长的成长，承认这使他感到“困惑和沮丧”。</p><p>这位以<a href="/tag/grammys">格莱美族人</a>为主导的艺术家与<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/benson-boone-beautiful-things-new-album-american-heart-1235288819/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>坐下来，这是其<em>未来音乐</em>问题的四个封面明星中的第一名。在与该出版物交谈时，“美丽的事物”杀手讨论了他的成长经历和他的宗教。</p><p>布恩（Boone）出生于门罗（Monroe），华盛顿（Washington），在耶稣基督后期圣徒教会中长大，他承认他与摩门教没有关系。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGg7ttcSa14/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 aut