="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3846067" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1.jpg" alt="在SXSW会议和奥斯汀城市范围的SXSW会议上，Benson Boone在音乐展览会的滚石乐队未来。 （由Stephen Olker/SXSW会议和节日通过Getty Images摄影）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Benson-Boone-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3846067" class="wp-caption-text">在SXSW会议和奥斯汀城市范围的SXSW会议上，Benson Boone在音乐展览会的滚石乐队未来。 （由Stephen Olker/SXSW会议和节日通过Getty Images摄影）</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-zuckerberg-did-benson-boone-cosplay-for-his-wifes-40th-birthday-3842479">马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）以前分享了他为妻子40岁生日布恩（Boone）打扮成布恩（Boone）的镜头</a>。</p><p> Meta Tycoon借了Boone的蓝色连身裤在生日聚会上为他的妻子Priscilla Chan博士演出。活动的录像显示，扎克伯格（Zuckerberg）急剧脱下正式服装以露出连身裤，就像布恩（Boone）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>上表演了“美丽的事物”，然后在舞台上踩踏，在现场乐队前表演。他还像布恩一样在钢琴上唱歌。</p><p>在其他地方，布恩以前在格莱美奖中为他“积极地”抓住crot的格莱美奖<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benson-boone-apologises-for-crotch-grab-during-grammys-3834514">为病毒时刻道歉</a>。</p><p>本<a href="https://www.nme.com">梅（NME）</a>首先出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benson-boone-on-growing-up-as-a-mormon-i-was-always-confused-and-frustrated-3846051">本·布恩（Benson Boone）在成长为摩尔门（Mormon）时长大的</a>。</p> ;
孟买自行车俱乐部宣布英国亲密的热身日期，在所有积分东部2025年之前https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-annouse-innouse-incimate-uk-harmindimate-uc--------------- before-all-pofer-east-east-2025-3846052?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = bombay-byclecle-club-annouse-incuk-uk-uk-up-up-up-dates-before-the-pofter-pofter-points-east-east-2025Liberty Dunworth Thu, 13 Mar 2025 16:47:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3846052 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="吉他手兼歌手杰克·斯特德曼（Jack Steadman）的孟买自行车俱乐部" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们将加入MacCabees参加今年的伦敦音乐节</p><p>孟买后自行车俱乐部宣布，在East 2025的所有点首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-announce-intimate-uk-warm-up-dates-before-all-points-east-2025-3846052">之前，英国的亲密预热日期</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="吉他手兼歌手杰克·斯特德曼（Jack Steadman）的孟买自行车俱乐部" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bombay@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">孟买自行车俱乐部</a>宣布了几个亲密的英国现场表演，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">East 2025的所有角度</a>都达到了插槽。查看以下详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bombay-bicycle-club-my-big-day-review-3517729">孟买自行车俱乐部 - “我的大日子”评论：独立英雄邀请达蒙·阿尔巴恩和查卡·汗</a></strong></li></ul><p>新的日期全都出现在伦敦音乐节上的乐队老虎机上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-reveal-support-acts-for-all-points-east-2025-reunion-3807780">今年夏天在维多利亚公园与马卡比斯一起举行。</a></p><p>首先将在约克的巴比肯（Barbican）场地举行，并于8月22日举行。后者将于第二天晚上（8月23日）（8月23日）看到乐队在利物浦的山福德音乐厅（Mountford Hall）场地上登上舞台。</p><p>他们从先前确认的老虎机计划五月计划中进行，该乐队将于该月底在马德里的Tomavistas音乐节举行。</p><p>两次新英国演出的门票明天（3月14日）当地时间上午9点举行。每场演出的支持将来自前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/divorce-03-03-2025-3842855"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/divorce">离婚</a>，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbombay-bicycle-club-tickets%2Fartist%2F41055" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里访问</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHGYrrxNFT_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: fl