com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Aphex-Twin.-Credit-Mick-Hutson_Redferns-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Aphex-Twin.-Credit-Mick-Hutson_Redferns-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Aphex-Twin.-Credit-Mick-Hutson_Redferns-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Aphex-Twin.-Credit-Mick-Hutson_Redferns-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Aphex-Twin.-Credit-Mick-Hutson_Redferns-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Aphex Twin在发布了一系列服装后，为该品牌策划了191首歌的播放列表。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/aphex-twin-at-printworks-2549628-2549628"><b>伦敦Printworks的Aphex Twin：仍然是地球上最伟大的电子节目之一</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>两者之间的合作伙伴关系是Streetwear品牌的新春季/夏季2025系列的一部分，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-and-aphex-twin-team-up-for-windowlicker-collab-shirt-3839023">看到该品牌发行了一件独家制作的T恤，其中包括Aphex Twin的1999年1999年曲目“ Windowlicker”的标志性封面艺术</a>。</p><p> Aphex Twin，真名理查德·詹姆斯（Richard James）也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-and-supreme-collaboration-launches-more-products-including-new-coin-knife-3843580">通过品牌发布了夹克，帽子，球衣，T恤等。</a>现在，电子音乐家已经为Supreme制作了播放列表，由近200首歌曲组成，由大多数冷藏，低温的选择组成。</p><p>它的标题为[大多是柔和的]，其中包含来自海滩男孩，布莱恩·埃诺（Brian Eno），卡夫特维克（Kraftwerk），Squarepusher，Marvin Gaye，Delia Derbyshire和Ragga Twins的歌曲。最高播放列表还具有一个Aphex Twin Original，2014年的“ Xmas_evet1n”。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：aphex twin：[大多是柔和的]" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/3jfnlosjVZhBSZBqS2cJg7?si=2f3c213ed539474b&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> “ [大多数是柔和的]”可以在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLquC_HTqu_9a6jVZTvkYhh5qL0Sth9Jyq&amp;jct=UuJz0VjWwxJguWXtvg96Yg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>和<a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/3jfnlosjVZhBSZBqS2cJg7?si=0e1fff703c114763&amp;pt_success=1&amp;nd=1&amp;dlsi=95486747df184f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify</a>上流式传输。查看下面的艺术品，然后<a href="https://supreme.com/news/987" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查看Collaber Collection。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-announce-janes-addiction-fashion-collection-3808098">Supreme之前曾与音乐表演合作，包括与Jane的成瘾合作</a>，该成瘾于去年10月下降，并在2021年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/massive-attack-supreme-collaboration-2970668">以巨大的攻击风格服装系列</a>。</p><p>在此之前，有来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-smiths-inspired-fall-fashion-range-2535573">史密斯（Smiths）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-supreme-collection-featuring-velvet-underground-album-art-2548705">天鹅绒（Velvet）</a>等人的启发的收藏，2015年，Supreme Tap <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-29-1208369">Neil Young</a>进行了合作，出售了一件T恤，上面有一张Young本人穿着最高品牌衬衫的照片。</p><p>在其他Aphex Twin News中，早在12月，艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-surprise-releases-new-compilation-music-from-the-merch-desk-2016-2023-3822843">就惊喜发行了一份新的汇编，称为“来自Merch Desk（2016-2023）”</a> 。</p><p>他于2023年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-announces-new-ep-shares-first-track-blackbox-life-recorder-21f-3458933">在Room7 F760&#39;EP中发布了他的“ Blackbox Life Recorder 21F /”</a> ，这是他五年来的第一首新音乐。该系列还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-launches-new-augmented-reality-app-3484622">产生了自己的增强现实应用程序</a>。然后，他在第二个月份放弃了EP&#39;London 19.08.2023&#39;，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-and-bonobo-to-headline-field-day-2023-buy-tickets-3385769#:~:text=The%20date%20%E2%80%93%20August%2019%2C%202023,show%20in%202019%20at%20Printworks.">他在伦敦2023年的《田野日》（Field Day）的头条表演</a>相吻合。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-has-curated-a-191-song-playlist-as-part-of-his-supreme-collaboration-3845989">Aphex Twin帖子策划了191首歌的播放列表，作为他的最高合作的一部分，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
听Lizzo的毫无歉意的新单曲“仍然不好” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lizzos-unapologetic-new-single-still-bad-3846004?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-lizzos-unapologetic-new-single-still-badAnagricel Duran Thu, 13 Mar 2025 16:00:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3846004 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2025年3月12日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的Wiltern的Lizzo现实生活中的Lizzo。 （Christopher Polk/Billboard通过Getty Images摄影）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌标志着她即将发行的第五张专辑《现实生活中的爱》的第二张单曲</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lizzos-unapologetic-new-single-still-bad-3846004">收听Lizzo的毫无歉意的新单曲“ Still Bad”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2025年3月12日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的Wiltern的Lizzo现实生活中的Lizzo。 （Christopher Polk/Billboard通过Getty Images摄影）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Lizzo">Lizzo</a>分享了她即将发行的专辑“ Love In Real Life”中毫无歉意的新单曲“ Still Bad”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">lizzo  - “特别”评论：自信，自我授权的bops的快乐超级巨星升起</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌的特色是80年代风格的钥匙和头像拍手，而Lizzo表明她仍然像以往任何时候一样毫无歉意。 <em>“我不需要他。我需要喝一杯</em>。然后她喊道： <em>“毕竟，我仍然生存，我仍然很糟糕，宝贝，所以我不能抱怨。”</em></p><p> Lizzo以前在她的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG363mASsWz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=embed_video_watch_again" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram上有一个视频剪辑在她的跳舞和唱歌的曲目</a>上嘲笑“仍然很糟糕”，同时又唱着卷发和全红色的合奏。剪辑的位置标签为“您的新喜爱歌曲”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="lizzo-仍然很糟糕（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NDM9zFwok0A?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “仍然很糟糕”标志着Lizzo即将发行的第五张专辑《现实生活中的Love In Real》的第二个品尝者。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-music-video-for-lizzos-funky-indie-rock-comeback-single-love-in-real-life-3842164">之前发布了LP的冠军头单曲</a>。这张专辑的主打单曲Mark Mark Lizzo自2022年LP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">Specia</a> L”以来重返音乐。在撰写本文时，“现实生活中的爱”没有正式发布日期。新闻稿分享说：“本章全部涉及爱，生活和利佐。”</p><p>尼克·莱文（Nick Levine）在对“特别”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">四星级评论</a>中为<em>NME</em>写道：“也许不可避免地，考虑到Lizzo的压倒性积极信息，“ Special”有时会有些俗气。尽管如此，它还是不想抗拒的方式俗气的。 “<em>是你的生日吗，女孩？ /“因为你看起来像礼物</em>，”她在“生日女孩”上唱歌，这首歌几乎将您前进到酒吧，并向您命令您拍摄龙舌兰酒玫瑰的照片。</p><p> “在这个证据上，Lizzo确切地知道她是一名艺术家以及她想实现的目标：她是一个坏母狗，拥有令人难以置信的才华，使人们感觉良好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHG0a93vrEu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.2